      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Stephen Muggleton</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:160px;\"><a href=\"http://wp.doc.ic.ac.uk/shm/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/3e/Stephen_muggleton_photo_in_2010.jpg\" width=\"158\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Stephen_muggleton_photo_in_2010.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Stephen Muggleton <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Stephen H. Muggleton</b>,<br />\na British computer scientist, professor and head of <i>Computational Bioinformatics Laboratory</i> at <i>Department of Computing</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imperial_College_London\">Imperial College London</a>. \nHe received his B.Sc. in computer science at <a href=\"/University_of_Edinburgh\" title=\"University of Edinburgh\">University of Edinburgh</a> in 1982, and his Ph.D research on the topic <i>Inductive Acquisition of Expert Knowledge</i> was carried out at Edinburgh under the supervision of <a href=\"/Donald_Michie\" title=\"Donald Michie\">Donald Michie</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \nIn 1991, Stephen Muggleton introduced <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inductive_logic_programming\">Inductive logic programming</a> as a field of <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, which is particularly useful in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bioinformatics\">bioinformatics</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_language_processing\">natural language processing</a>, also applied to certain <a href=\"/Endgame\" title=\"Endgame\">chess endgames</a> like <a href=\"/KRK\" title=\"KRK\">KRK</a>. \nSince July 2000, Muggleton is Editor-in-chief of the <i>Machine Intelligence Series</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, founded by Michie who convened the first International Machine Intelligence Workshop at Edinburgh in 1965. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1986_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1986 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1986_...\">1986 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1986 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1986</b>). <i>Inductive Acquisition of Expert Knowledge</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/University_of_Edinburgh\" title=\"University of Edinburgh\">University of Edinburgh</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Donald_Michie\" title=\"Donald Michie\">Donald Michie</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1987</b>). <i>Duce, an oracle-based approach to constructive induction</i>. Proceedings of the 10th IJCAI Conference, Milano, Italy. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/%7Eshm/Papers/ijcai87.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1988</b>). <i>Inductive Acquisition of Chess Strategies</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/%7Eshm/MI/mi11.html\">Machine Intelligence 11</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Bain\" title=\"Michael Bain\">Michael Bain</a>, <a href=\"/Jean_Hayes_Michie\" title=\"Jean Hayes Michie\">Jean Hayes Michie</a>, <a href=\"/Donald_Michie\" title=\"Donald Michie\">Donald Michie</a> (<b>1989</b>). <i>An Experimental Comparison of Human and Machine Learning Formalisms</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/icml/ml1989.html#MuggletonBMM89\">6. ML 1989</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/ml6paper.pdf\">pdf</a> </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i>Inductive Acquisition of Expert Knowledge</i>. Turing Institute Press. Addison-Wesley</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/f/Feng:Cao.html\">Cao Feng</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i>Efficient Induction of Logic Programs</i>. Proceedings of the First International Workshop on Algorithmic Learning Theory (ALT90) (eds. S. Arikaxa, S. Soto, S. Ohsuya, and T. Yokomari), pp. 368-381. Ohmsha, Tokyo, Japan.</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1991</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF03037089\">Inductive Logic Programming</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/journal/354/8/4/page/1\">New Generation Computing</a>, Vol. 8, No. 4, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/%7Eshm/Papers/ilp.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ashwin_Srinivasan\" title=\"Ashwin Srinivasan\">Ashwin Srinivasan</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Bain\" title=\"Michael Bain\">Michael Bain</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Distinguishing exceptions from noise in non-monotonic Learning</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.york.ac.uk/ILP-events/ILP-1992/\">ILP92</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/fd37/06021c2230104a6f89cc93b341b7896e26bb.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Michael_Bain\" title=\"Michael Bain\">Michael Bain</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>Learning Optimal Chess Strategies</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/%7Eshm/MI/mi13.html\">Machine Intelligence 13</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>Bayesian Inductive Logic Programming</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/colt/colt1994.html\">COLT 1994</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/bayesian.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Applications of Inductive Logic Programming</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 38, No. 11, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/cacm.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-63494-0_65\">Learning from Positive Data</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ilp/ilp96.html\">ILP 1996</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a href=\"/Donald_Michie\" title=\"Donald Michie\">Donald Michie</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-62560-7_51\">Machine Intelligibility and the Duality Principle</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/btlab/btlab1997.html\">Software Agents and Soft Computing 1997</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F3-540-49292-5_5\">Knowledge Discovery in Biological and Chemical Domains</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/dis/dis98.html\">Discovery Science 1998</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Scientific Knowledge Discovery Using Inductive Logic Programming</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 42, No. 11, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/cacm2.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Inductive Logic Programming: Issues, Results and the Challenge of Learning Language in Logic</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_(journal)\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 114, No. 1-2, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/aij99.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Bain\" title=\"Michael Bain\">Michael Bain</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Analogical Prediction</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ilp/ilp99.html\">ILP 1999</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/ap.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Michael_Bain\" title=\"Michael Bain\">Michael Bain</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a href=\"/Ashwin_Srinivasan\" title=\"Ashwin Srinivasan\">Ashwin Srinivasan</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Generalising Closed World Specialisation: A Chess End Game Application</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/5c3b/c747c01e8aba82fd288db52faac2f7fb30a3.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-36468-4_13\">Learning Structure and Parameters of Stochastic Logic Programs</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ilp/ilp2002.html\">ILP 2002</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/diffslp.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>Machine Learning for Systems Biology</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ilp/ilp2005.html\">ILP 2005</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/mlsysbio.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>Towards Chemical Universal Turing Machines</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-2006\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI 2006</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/chemturing.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-88190-2_6\">From ILP to PILP</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/sbia/sbia2008.html\">SBIA 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Aline_Paes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Aline Paes (page does not exist)\">Aline Paes</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=V%C3%ADtor_Santos_Costa&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Vítor Santos Costa (page does not exist)\">Vítor Santos Costa</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerson_Zaverucha&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gerson Zaverucha (page does not exist)\">Gerson Zaverucha</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-642-13840-9_12\">Chess Revision: Acquiring the Rules of Chess Variants through FOL Theory Revision from Examples</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ilp/ilp2009.html\">ILP 2009</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/paeschess.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-642-16327-2_2\">Knowledge Mining Biological Network Models</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ifip12/iip2010.html\">IIP 2010</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#LDRaedt\" title=\"Mathematician\">Luc De Raedt</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#DPoole\" title=\"Mathematician\">David Poole</a>, <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Flach\">Peter A. Flach</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://research.nii.ac.jp/~inoue/official/content_e.html\">Katsumi Inoue</a>, <a href=\"/Ashwin_Srinivasan\" title=\"Ashwin Srinivasan\">Ashwin Srinivasan</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s10994-011-5259-2\">ILP turns 20 - Biography and future challenges</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Machine_Learning_(journal)\">Machine Learning</a>, Vol. 86, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Alan Turing and the development of Artificial Intelligence</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/journals/aicom/aicom27.html\">AI Communications, Vol. 27</a>, No. 1, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/TuringAI_1.pdf\">pdf</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Alan_Turing\" title=\"Alan Turing\">Alan Turing</a>, <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">Artificial Intelligence</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=fZinJ_AAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Sumit Gulwani</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://josephorallo.webs.upv.es/\">José Hernández-Orallo</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://emanuel.kitzelmann.org/academia/\">Emanuel Kitzelmann</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.uni-bamberg.de/en/cogsys/schmid-ute/\">Ute Schmid</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/zorn/\">Benjamin Zorn</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i>Inductive programming meets the real world</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 58, No. 11, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/indprogreal.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stephen Muggleton</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Meta-Interpretive Learning: Achievements and Challenges</i>. Invited Paper, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ruleml/ruleml2017.html\">RuleML+RR 2017</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~shm/Papers/rulemlabs.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wp.doc.ic.ac.uk/shm/\">Stephen H. Muggleton</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Muggleton\">Stephen Muggleton from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=166206\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Stephen Muggleton</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/science/2007/jul/10/uk.obituaries1\">Obituary - Donald Michie</a> by Stephen Muggleton, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian\">The Guardian</a>, Tuesday July 10 2007</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stephen_Muggleton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wp.doc.ic.ac.uk/shm/\">Stephen H. Muggleton</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#c